"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"[![Andre Cronje](https://miro.medium.com/fit/c/56/56/2\\\\*Vjiwqoib1HcKLdkM1xwp_g.jpeg)](https://andrecronje.medium.com/?source=post_page-----715f77051261--------------------------------)\\n\\nRarity Gold is an ERC20 for NFTs :)\\n\\nAny game economy needs currency, but again, this gold shouldnâ€™t be gated, nor should it turn into a speculative asset. As per wealth per level guidelines, summoners can claim gold after each level advancement. Gold is however not owned by the address, nor is it a standard ERC20, but instead, gold is an ERC20 owned by the summoner (the NFT itself). Summoners can trade between each other as per normal (with `transfer`), and auction houses / merchants / stores can be created via `transferFrom`), but only a summoner can be an owner of gold.\\n\\nA summoner can claim gold starting from level 2 and every level thereafter. Gold will be the default currency for auction houses, merchants, npcs, quests, and stores implemented in the default universe.\\n\\n**Technical**\\n\\n[0x2069B76Afe6b734Fb65D1d099E7ec64ee9CC76B2](https://ftmscan.com/address/0x2069b76afe6b734fb65d1d099e7ec64ee9cc76b2#code)\\n\\n[Github](https://github.com/andrecronje/rarity/blob/main/gold.sol)\\n\",\"timestamp\":1634229377,\"title\":\"Rarity Gold (with a twist) - Andre Cronje - Medium\"},\"digest\":\"HPaEV03cNmna3RhCP33TJdhBLpdV41e4xRFH0og-5Zo\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0x770De711ED4629790fD8Ce95C86C812149a6CCE5\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"xG2u6rrmwdQt9L-g0s84-FKbyCEgapS6u32FBllN42M\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"WjPuEPBnveYFgTR7nNV521MvWALprDLUbqvV3VJBm_o\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"MpKxjyqqIMTblxPf0R46PotBxeeUB6q1VpbJExExZA4bxSLCjGoPXG5zPt_BL5ONeOS3cEJUU8w5peWzGeOBFA\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0x4187ab60ac0b28a7d6e255357018e801c16cb756119bf3119ae0196481fba5ec56d5f59800742046b4b633614c34e8e267aa884c15c0ca54b06152e0f8e160211b\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I